data.description: Almost  new townhouse with fenced in yard and detached garage You will fall in love with this end unit townhome. Primary bedroom is in the main floor along with a beautiful kitchen that has stainless appliances and granite countertops. This home has a modern, open floorplan. The upstairs has a fabulous, large flex space that can be used as an office, media room or play room along with two other gracious sized bedrooms. Walkable to tons of shopping and restaurants.
